{"title": "How Do I Change the Default Appointment Duration?", "body": "Follow these steps to change the default appointment duration:\nClick the More tab and select Settings from the drop-down menu\nClick Settings\nClick Appointments\nSelect the name of the Practice\nClick Calendar Units under the Practice category and select the default appointment duration\nClick Save/Update to apply the changes\nThe default appointment duration has now been updated, and the default time slots will be reflected on the appointment calendar.\nNOTE: If these changes are not immediately reflected on your calendar, refresh the page or sign out and sign back in.\nEditing or Removing Existing Appointment Types"}